Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shimogamo Shrine is located 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the triangular area surrounded by the Takano and Kamo rivers. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\pos(1200,30)\c&H0E0506&\bord0}"Lake Biwa"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although there are mountains of shrines with noble lineages in Kyoto, 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&HD9B5F6&\3c&HBF3946&}"Kamo River"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&HEEEBA4&\3c&HBF3946&}"Takano River"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimogamo Shrine is one of the foremost 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H52F3EB&\3c&HBF3946&\fad(0,200)}"Shimogamo Shrine"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,among the ones that existed prior to the Heian period. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though scores of visitors go there throughout the year 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H97E7ED&\be4\pos(720,50)}"God of matchmaking Aioi Shrine"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to receive matchmaking and all kinds of other blessings from the gods, 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,few know that a small ramen cart appears in the vicinity each and every night. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Neko Ramen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rumor is it uses actual cats to make the broth, 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but whether that's true or not cannot be ascertained. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the taste is unmatched. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a person of Shimogamo Yuusuisou, yes? 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact I am a resident of Shimogamo Yuusuisou. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:00:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and...? 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also live there. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimogamo Yuusuisou is a boarding house behind Eizan Demachiyanagi Station, 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's apparently exactly the same as it was since it was rebuilt after it disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during the violence of the final days of the Tokugawa shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for the light leaking out the windows, it would be no different than ruins, 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when I visited there at the introduction of the University Co-op at the start of school,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder I thought I'd accidentally stumbled into Kowloon City. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered that I have spotted this queer, curious fellow quite a number of times. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a god of Shimogamo Shrine. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My proper name is Kamotaketsunuminokami. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kamotake? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamotaketsunominokamo. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me say it twice. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the second time was different... 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.05,0:01:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents' names, how you were always throwing up and making sour smells as a baby, 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your nickname during elementary school, the middle school cultural festival, 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your fleeting first love during high school, the first time you watched an adult video, 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your life as a ronin, and your lazy, idle days spent after entering college. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After suffering romantic disappointment in the club of your dreams, unable to open up to people, 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before long you started getting in the way of people's path to love. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why have you spent these two years in such a timid state? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:01:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because Ozu... 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept that you have had your soul somewhat dirtied by the influence of Ozu. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is not all, is it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The past two years go rambling through my brain like swaying paper lanterns. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the sacred woods of Shimogamo Shrine, of all places, 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my delicate heart was seized by painful memories, and... 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H86EEF6&}"Ahhhh!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what I wanted to scream out, but I restrained myself like a gentleman. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-None of your business. It's got nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will soon be Kannazuki. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must travel to Izumo once again. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is our job, yes, but it is quite a lot of work, and don't make light of the train fare. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this age we just toss everyone's proposals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into the wooden box for "already inspected" with hardly a look. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet as I am a serious fellow, 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but to be deep in thought, scratching my head 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking about which two people would be most suited for each other, 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,almost like a matrimonial agency. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woe is me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't follow in the slightest. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When fall comes we gather at Izumo, 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and decide the relationships of men and women. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the name Akashi-san, whom you know. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here are you and the name Ozu. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand what? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're even stupider than I thought. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a god of matchmaking, 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am preparing to match this woman you know, Akashi-san, with someone. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's between you and Ozu-kun. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you desire, come to my room. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimogamo Yuusuisou, room 210.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}This strange fellow is saying he is trying to tie Akashi-san to either Ozu or me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H6C00C6&\fad(200,0)}J{\c&H000000&}-pwq
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in high school I didn't participate in any club activities 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and just stayed cooped up with a bunch of other layabout guys. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I was a brand-spanking new freshman university student. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and countless doors to the mystical treasure that is known as 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that "rose-colored campus life" lay open before me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was half-swooned with glee. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one I chose was... 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,1400)\bord0\c&H6B2F4B&}"Cupid"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the raven-haired maidens working up an invigorating sweat, 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would begin the rally of love! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what I, a fool beyond all help, had thought. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first summer. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My still-as-of-yet rose-colored self was cut to the quick by that which is called reality. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making 100 friends wouldn't be so bad, or so I frivolously thought, 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was soon made aware that just how difficult casually getting to know other people could be. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish of a rally unfulfilled, I was not even able to hit back, 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my serves were left unreturned. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried training myself to be sociable and easy-going, 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I wasn't part of the conversation to begin with. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I realized I had to be sociable in order to be included in the conversation, 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was already too late. I had lost my place among the circle. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:06:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was then that an ominous man stood beside me with a face of ill portent. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some messenger from hell that only delicate little me can see? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say some pretty mean things. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry, I am your compatriot! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first contact with Ozu, as well as worst contact. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's quite a contrast, isn't it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should mix it up over there myself. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\3c&H682221&\c&H60CE86&\fad(0,200)}"Shimogamo Shrine"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where the Kamo and Takano rivers join 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,below the Shimogamo Shrine is referred to as the "Kamo River Delta," 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is widely used as a party location for celebrating the beginning of summer. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H682221&\c&H5E39A9&\fad(200,0)}"Us, Concealed"  {\c&H73B2DA&}"Party Area"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu is in the same year I am. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8 in 10 people who saw him in the dark would mistake him for a youkai, 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(1032,208)\c&HD79F7C&\3c&H220C51&}"Hates vegetables"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H8BCCAD&\3c&H220C51&\fs32\pos(842,412)}"Grades\N dangerously low"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H220C51&\c&H8ACBAC&\pos(272,46)}"Selfish"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H220C51&\c&H218FE2&\pos(189,543)}"No pride"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H220C51&\c&HBC84E5&\pos(491,518)}"Lazy"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H220C51&\c&H238BDE&\pos(900,100)}"Picks on the weak"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H220C51&\c&HD69D7B&\pos(350,472)}"The devil"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H220C51&\c&H208DE1&\pos(990,257)}"Sucks up to the strong"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H220C51&\c&H89CCAD&\fs30\pos(321,211)}"Doesn't care as\N long as it's funny"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H220C51&\fs30\c&HBC84E5&\pos(107,305)}"Fast at\N running\N away"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H220C51&\fs30\c&HD39E7B&\pos(1085,533)}"Worthless\N character"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the remaining two could be convinced of it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating the unhappiness of the others as a topping on his rice, 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's a man with seriously not a single point of praise. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul would have surely stayed unblemished were it not for having met him. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you gonna turn on me? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just joking with you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop touching me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the night breeze is so chilly... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lonely bastard! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Why does it have to be you next to me instead of a raven-haired maiden? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look. Akashi-san came, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, over there. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in the engineering department, so maybe she's designing for Birdman or something. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, maybe we should call it off for today... 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get Akashi-san mixed up in this. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?\N What happened to your pride as a "Black Cupid"? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure I have my pride, but to someone from the outside, this just looks like... 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to let your conviction bend because you're worried about what other people think? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I, who have dedicated both my body and soul, am not a person such as that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not here today precisely because you bare this loneliness and isolation? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the ones that have lost sight of reality! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must bring the hammer down upon those who have lost themselves among frivolous dreams! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, without further ado! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear ye, hear ye! For we are the ones who hinder love! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now rain the heavens down upon you merrymaking ladies and gentlemen! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Id... iot... 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we may be idiots, but you guys should watch out for us! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bottle rocket fireworks are for the purpose of rocketing up into the night sky. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H99999C&}"Bottle rockets, roman candles and firecrackers are not allowed"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing things like holding them in your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aiming them at people, or using them to bomb people over rivers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having a peaceful harmonious party is quite not allowed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your ground! Counterattack! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn barbarians! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one shallow river! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna smack you good! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ozu, they're not all out! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I had met Ozu it was just cutting, cutting, and more cutting
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the red threads that stretched across the circle like at Yasui-konpiragu. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H000D1D&\bord0}"Fatty"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At these activities Ozu was ingenious, 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there were even villainous rumors 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that there was no personal information we did not know and make use of, 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that we would scatter oil and then light fires, 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H000D1D&\bord0}"Baldy"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and whether that was true or not it was spread around 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it was an environment where we were set up as guys 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who constantly enjoyed blazing scenes of carnage here and there inside the circle. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like some incarnation of evil, a disgrace among all homo sapiens. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after we were kicked out of the circle, 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we did not let our activities slacken, we expanded globally, 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cloaked as gods of death the evil name of the "Black Cupids" roared throughout the land. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a maiden in love in the east we'd say "Give up on that freak," 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or for a man in the west worried about one-sided love we'd advise 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just give up, it's no use." 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the spark of love was sprinkled in the south, we'd immediately pour water on it, 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's said love in the north is impossible to begin with. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes our victims came close to drowning us in the canals of Lake Biwa, 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surrounded the boarding house, made me hide in a manga cafe in Kitashirakawa, 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or cried at me in the middle of Konoe Street when I spoke too frankly. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't lose, I couldn't lose, 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though I was sure that losing would have let me and everyone else be happier! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except for Ozu. I could care less if he's happy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I was walking, catching my breath after having run all the way to Kiyamachi, 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under the overhang of someone's house 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was caught by an old woman who emitted a suspiciously ghoulish aura. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unplaceable aura was persuasive, and thinking logically, 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was no way that the fortune-telling of a creature 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who emits such an aura could be anything but spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is a face of extreme impatience... You are unsatisfied. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel that you are not blessed with a situation 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where you can make the most of your talents. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's exactly right! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense your fiercely earnest talent. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly did I tip my hat to the old woman's keen insight. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To perceive my good sense and talents in an instant and yet be so very unassuming,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like how a master always hides their true ability, it made even me forget where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I sense there is an opportunity you can't let pass by. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An opportunity? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As in an excellent chance. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know what it means... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This opportunity is always dangling in front of your eyes. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must grab this opportunity and act on it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still somewhat vague. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you be more specific? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you do not! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will walk this life as now, ever unchanging. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 1,000 yen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't answered anything yet! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing the lost lamb? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of yours, Ozu-kun? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shameless bastard! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell are you popular all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's just uncalled for. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Force feeding me such a bundle of fungi? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with these ribbed bits? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the dental hygienist at the dentist I go to. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked totally drunk and asked me out for drinks. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentist? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you've never had a young lady like that stick her fingers 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in your mouth your entire life, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring me down to your level. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you visited the god of matchmaking at the Shimogamo Shrine. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to do it once for fun! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, what do you think of Akashi-san? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's between you and Ozu-kun. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I think? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought I was the only person unfortunate enough 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to actually be able to comprehend a human being as dumb as yourself, but... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shush, you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she might go out with you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an opportunity! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd much rather have a beautiful raven-haired maiden 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that makes you go "whoa..." than someone who is able to comprehend a person such as myself. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so selfish? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're still hung up on being dumped by Kohinata-san? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we were freshmen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say not that name in my presence. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll become happy in your place. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this opportunity. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now see here. Akashi-san is not interested in you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that depressed look. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray for your victory. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you I've wasted my perfectly lovely college life. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I think you're also to blame for that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it doesn't matter which path you took, 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd keep ending up right where you are now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, once I met you I put all my efforts into making you no good. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you haunt me so? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the way I show my love! We're connected by the black thread of fate, after all.  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\c&HA567D6&}"The Japan Trench"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A chill went down my spine as a fearsome phantom rose into my mind. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, if you want to eat any more, please hurry. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san, why are you here? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are pretty dense, aren't you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the usual place for the after-party, yes? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Birdman Circle is camped out over there. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't eaten meat in a while so if you don't mind... 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat after a party? Do they have no pride as agricultural people? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ozu? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already ran out the back door. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You escape too, Senpai. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard's left me behind again! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will handle the bill, so go out the back. That's what I came to say. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your debt. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about the debt, just keep your promise. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Hurry and leave, I have to get back. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met Akashi-san the previous year during a part time job at the Shimogamo used book fair. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A year younger than I, said to be in the engineering department, 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and meticulously prepared at anything and everything she does, 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it felt like one stare from her eyes and even a shoplifter would stay their hand. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you do on vacations, Akashi-san? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to tell you something like that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that she was not someone who was asked her weekend plans. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent her off with a fiery cheer of\N "You just keep doing things your own way!" 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Don't just barge in my room! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you just stroll on in... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Castella. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it, so chill out. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You giving someone something? That's rare... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get any lonelier than eating a giant Castella all by yourself. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pining for a taste of a person's love... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out! I'm busy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably came to visit the person in this boarding house known as "the master." 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Castella is surely the leftovers. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, just as Ozu said, a Castella like this is to be eaten together with someone. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most definitely not Ozu. Perhaps with Akashi-san... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I was surprised that Akashi-san's name came to mind. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that strange man who called himself a god and said he was heading out to Izumo 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to decide the relationship between man and woman seriously be telling the truth? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kannazuki. In other words, the 10th lunar month. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The myriad gods gather at Izumo, leaving vacant the various lands. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HB9FBF9&\3c&H743C46&\fad(400,0)}"Izumo"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite well known. Even I know that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among those gods there are sure to be some of suitable peculiarity. That is not the issue. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question I have often pondered is for what reason all those gods would gather at Izumo. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And written right there it says that, at Izumo, after a boisterous and outspoken argument, 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the myriad gods decide the relationships between man and woman! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\c&H45B6AC&}"Don't they have anything better to do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'd ascertained the truth, 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be best for me to climb the stairs and see this god face to face. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that god from yesterday went... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha ha, I got you good! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or something, I couldn't stand it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd surely end up cursing myself and spending the second half of my life in a right mess. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that man is really a god, 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not like I'm burning with passionate love; 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would go against my beliefs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to seek the comfort of a stranger from this transient loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not because I scorn those inexcusable students
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who cannot bear the isolation and greedily seek out others 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I ran to the name of limitless notoriety as "one who hinders love"? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guise of a barren, agonizing, wretched life... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have not I finally reaped the victory close at hand from the endless number of defeats? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would I, the one who hinders love, forgive myself for changing the way I live? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:16:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will it end with me proving entertainment to the gods as the spider's thread to which I cling snaps? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll become happy in your place. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I don't think Akashi-san would be fooled by a freaky youkai like Ozu, 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like her compassion may be deep enough to find a monstrous man like him intriguing. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this continues and Ozu and Akashi-san become friendly with each other, 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this will no longer be a problem of my own love; 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will become entangled with Akashi-san's future. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like even my reason was crumbling to pieces like the Castella before me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose to pining for love! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The taste is definitely unmatched, 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but unfortunately no one knows where they'll set up. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ramen stand that comes and goes as it pleases. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go there quite often, yes, Senpai? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have a good nose. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm hungry, if I cock my ear I can hear Neko Ramen's wind chime. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to try eating there as well. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go, Akashi-san! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I s-s-squished it‚ I squished it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. I am not fond of moths. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are called Mochiguman, and they come in sets of five, but I have lost one. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not! As this Earth is round, you are sure to meet once again! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or if you'd like, I'll help search for it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather you take me to Neko Ramen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's a promise. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise? Ah, that's it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After careful analysis, indeed over-analysis of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I calmly execute a perfect countermeasure. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I'm a man who doesn't hesitate to analyze to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where a perfect countermeasure becomes out of reach. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Analyzing the number of different patterns of Akashi-san's life and my life, 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I quickly came to a conclusion as to who should become happy, and who should not. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the most vexing question of all was whether I, 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who had hindered the path of love for countless people, 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could at this juncture change the way I live. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result of the life or death death struggle between love and reason that occurred within me, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stumbled in my sleep-deprived state to knock on door 210. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give her to Ozu! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Akashi-san to me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Good, wait here a moment. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Understood, yes... 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me before 8 PM on the east side of Kamo-oohashi. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep moving! Keep moving! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stopping on top of the bridge is dangerous! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so today is Gozan. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you will cross this Kamo-oohashi. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you do, Akashi-san will come walking from the other side. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike up a conversation about something and ask her out on a rendezvous. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I refuse! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your whining. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something isn't right here! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to Izumo and being a matchmaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sort of preparation is also important. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing but a frontal attack! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining and get out there. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything until now is water under the bridge! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to push forward toward that rose-colored campus life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, good evening. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You escaped safely last night? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, yeah... 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here for Gozan? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes yes. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That went well. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for today. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to come this far despite 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,learning not even the slightest bit about running the path of love! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:19:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was plenty! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just thought something like "that's enough for today," didn't you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't defy the words of a god, hurry up and run along the path of love! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying this was all your plot? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made a wish to the god of matchmaking, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your help! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to grab this opportunity! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't make a serious move right now, I'm jumping! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do my love life and you jumping have anything to do with each other? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too sure myself. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu-san! The river is swollen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will die if you jump in. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn traitor! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got nowhere to run, Ozu! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge for the fireworks? But, this is... 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu-senpai, have you done some more mischief? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You evil, good-for-nothing... 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a friend of his? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I don't know Ozu at all... 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't shake off the feeling of regret
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for choosing tennis circle "Cupid" in front of that fateful clock tower. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If then I had chosen some other circle I would have surely spent quite a different two years. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I could have grasped 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the mystical treasure that is known as that "rose-colored campus life". 
